The paper deals with physical layer security and wireless communication networks, which are topics that fall under the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) sub-categories. The use of mmWave frequency bands and multi-antenna transmission techniques also suggests that the paper could be relevant to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the optimization approach proposed in the paper involves a trade-off between resource availability and performance, which could be relevant to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
